name: Gaia
description: My contribution to the event #HENthousand - Traditional art, painting with acrylic paint and India ink on wooden canvas, stone dust texture on trunks and leaves, and clouds with marble dust texture. Year 2019 - Dimension: 100x39cm - By iagods - tt @iagods_ / ig @iagods_artes - Minha contribuição para o evento #HENthousand - Arte tradicional, pintura com tinta acrílica e nanquim sobre tela de madeira, textura de pó de pedra nos troncos e folhas, e nuvens com textura de pó de mármore. Ano de 2019 - Dimensão: 100x39cm - tt @iagods_ / ig @iagods_artes
